<section class="sectionbody">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-12">
        <div class="descriphold">
          <h1 class="headingholding">It is very necessary to do digital marketing!</h1>
          <p style="font-weight: 700;">Doing digital marketing means connecting to your your customers and potential customers. Every business has to do that in order to be successful.</p>
          <p style="font-weight: 300; text-align: left;">
           In this day and age, every business needs a proper digital marketing sstrategy in order to succeed online. Digital marketing is when businneses use channels like search engines, social media and email to reach out to their customers and potential customers and clients. Marketing has always been about connecting with your audience at the right place at the right time. Today, our customers and potential customers spend majority of their time on the phone and on the internet. This means we have to meet them at where they are already spending their time; on facebook, whatsapp, instagram, searching on google, and other websites and avenues that bring them online. These potential customers are to be harvested with a funnel based system. With a good product it is very easy to grow your business to over million Ghana Cedis. <strong>Do not miss out on an opportunity to massively grow your business..</strong> Fill the form on your left and lets start talking about your digital marketing strategy!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-5 col-md-12">
        <div class="ctahold">
          <h1 class="landingheader" style="font-weight: bold; text-align: center; color: white; font-size: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px;">Kindly fill this form.</h1>

       <%= form_for(@potential) do |f| %>
  <div class="form-group">
    <div class="form-group">
    <label style="font-weight: bold; color: white;">Name</label>
    <input type="text" name="potential[name]" id="potential_name" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Name">
  </div>
    <label style="font-weight: bold; color: white;">Email</label>
    <input type="email" name="potential[email]" id="potential_email" class="form-control" placeholder="Email Address">
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label style="font-weight: bold; color: white;">Phone Number</label>
    <input type="text" name="potential[phone]" id="potential_phone" class="form-control" placeholder="Your Phone number">
  </div>
  <div class="form-group">
    <label style="font-weight: bold; color: white;">Organization's Name</label>
    <input type="text" name="potential[orgname]" id="potential_orgname" class="form-control" placeholder="Organization's Name">
  </div>
  <input type="hidden" name="potential[digim]" id="potential_digim" value="digital marketing">
  <div class="form-group">
    <label style="font-weight: bold; color: white;">Any Objectives in mind?</label>
   <textarea class="form-control" name="potential[goal]" id="potential_goal" rows="3" placeholder="Increase my sales by 45%, Get new clients every week, etc"></textarea>
  </div>
  <br>
       <p style="color: #fff; text-align: center;">Response time is usually within an hour.</p> 
        <p style="text-align: center;"><button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary websubmit btn-lg">Send Marketing Enquiry</button></p>
      </div>
       
      
      <% end %>
